name: Furry Eeveelution LoRA
description:
The eeveelution family LoRA base on Yiffy-e18 training.

You can use on all Yiffy-e18 mixed models.

Also include "sky forme shaymin" and "absol", because they're eevee-like.

If you want to try "feral" type, use Yiffy-e18 model with 512x512px and put "anthro" in negative prompt.

This is a LoRA model, you will need new version Automatic's 1111 SD-WebUI or additional-networks extension

Use e621 tags like Yiffy-e18, no underscore, Stop at CLIP layers=1

Best setting = [network strength:0.5~0.8, CFG:4-7]
